title: Taj Burrow in VonZipper Pinch Sunglasses
description:
Story: Some say that big things come in small packages. Get a grip and give yourself a Pinch, because this modern classic is too good to be true.

Specs: VonZipper Pinch sunglasses are handmade in Italy; the frame is crafted from nylon grilamid and held together with stainless steel optical hinges. The base 6 spherical impact resistant polycarbonate lenses will protect your eyes with 100% UV protection.
